  "title": "1 Year Contract Payroll Assistant - REDHILL ( Last Day Pay Team)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Liaise with Institutional HR for necessary instructions & documents required for payroll processing.</li><li>Perform monthly payroll computation of various cost centers.</li><li>To be involved in month-end closing and accounts reconciliation.</li><li>Process employees' claims, IR8A, and all other related tax forms and filings.</li><li>Responsible for CPF contribution/refund.</li><li>Attend to enquiries from employees.</li><li>Handle ad-hoc activities as and when requested.</li></ul><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Diploma in any discipline with at least 3 years’ relevant Payroll experience for Senior Assistant Executive.</li><li>Meticulous with an eye for detail</li><li>A team player with a positive attitude and customer-oriented mindset</li><li>Strong interpersonal, communication, and analytical skills</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office applications</li><li>Hands-on experience with SAP system and/or shared service payroll experience will be an added advantage</li></ul><p>For interested candidate, please email your resumes to denyse.tan@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p><br /></p><p>Denyse Nicole Tan Shuqin (#HDT)</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>CEI No: R1333503</p><p>Company EA license : 99C4599</p>",
